&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Removal of Obstacle Stones&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Hunt Carreg&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;The collaborators around here will study the crystals you brought, so you don't have to worry. Meanwhile, let's start with another task. If you go into Tulach Dungeon, the monsters made by stones will try to stop you. 

Have you ever heard the name Carreg? If you look closely, you can see that they are made by pieces of the dungeon. Vicious draug probably regulate them by using something like Devil's Beads. 

To keep our study up to date, I think we have to find something from the stones. Let's slay them at the entrance. Then Go for it! 

&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;In the underground of Tulach Dungeon, there are many dangerous monsters. You have to be careful and make sure you know where you're going. You might have to go there again.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Very good! Even though they are just stones, they must be pouring with sweat. Let's see what the next mission is. This is big news!&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
