How is the offer? .&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Not bad, right? If you get the sting, come to the pub and find me. So who offered this request? Hohoho... I will tell you when you finish.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Did you bring everything I've requested? Ahh, so it's in the bag huh? Here is the payment that I've promised.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
